    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330160/extras/3c78e889641e17273b93541895ed3230.poster.avif?t=1770287880\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330160/extras/3c78e889641e17273b93541895ed3230.webm?t=1770287880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330160/extras/3c78e889641e17273b93541895ed3230.mp4?t=1770287880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>再试一次是一款回合制的roguelike游戏，您的牌组由扑克牌筹码组成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个筹码代表一个独立的动作。这些筹码可以增加或减少牌值，改变花色等等。升级您的牌组并收集新的、更强大的筹码，具有独特的能力，以创造独特的组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 具有不同属性的扑克牌筹码</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 英雄升级系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 许多独特的遗物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 具有特殊攻击的英雄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330160/extras/c52d01c452393c8bb95490bda772d4e2.poster.avif?t=1770287880\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330160/extras/c52d01c452393c8bb95490bda772d4e2.webm?t=1770287880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330160/extras/c52d01c452393c8bb95490bda772d4e2.mp4?t=1770287880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
